@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-bytecore#> .
@prefix bytestar: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix bc: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-bytecore#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-bytecore>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar ByteCore ABI Ontology" ;
  rdfs:comment "Contracts & ABIs shared across A, F, E, and Fabricators." .

### ABI & Schema artifacts
bc:KernelABI, bc:CrystalEnvelopeABI, bc:DispatchTableABI, bc:PulseSchema, bc:SPSCABI a owl:Class .
bc:LOUDSLayoutABI, bc:MPHFLayoutABI, bc:XORLayoutABI a owl:Class .

### Content addressing & manifests
bc:Manifest a owl:Class .
bc:hasDigest a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bc:Manifest ; rdfs:range xsd:hexBinary .
bc:toolchainLock a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bc:Manifest ; rdfs:range xsd:string .

### Contracts linkage
bc:conformsTo a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain bytestar:Subsystem ; rdfs:range [
  a owl:Class ; owl:unionOf ( bc:KernelABI bc:CrystalEnvelopeABI bc:DispatchTableABI bc:PQCTrait ) ] .

### PQC trait
bc:PQCTrait a owl:Class .
bc:providesVerify a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bc:PQCTrait ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
bc:providesSign   a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bc:PQCTrait ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
bc:providesKeygen a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bc:PQCTrait ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .